				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%AFc-chinh-B%E1%BA%AFc-quy-ch%C3%AD-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-m%E1%BA%B7c-ch%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%B3ng-v%C3%A3ng-Phu-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A1c/poem-xRXhuUOmluK39LpCU7hkCA">Bắc chinh - Bắc quy chí Phụng Tường, mặc chế phóng vãng Phu Châu tác - 北征－北歸至鳳翔，墨制放往鄜州作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-03/poem-I9Biy9aiD-APGE-E5fhm0g">Cảm ngộ kỳ 03 - 感遇其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-16/poem-BNgl-5l_4eNXIeLJyIXT-g">Cảm ngộ kỳ 16 - 感遇其十六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81i-T%C3%A2n-Gi%C3%A1c-La-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/Cung-chi%C3%AAm-Kh%E1%BA%A3i-V%E1%BA%ADn-s%C6%A1n-t%C3%A1c-ca/poem-0v8a-sECBQEsigO1H1mK6Q">Cung chiêm Khải Vận sơn tác ca - 恭瞻啟運山作歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81i-T%C3%A2n-Gi%C3%A1c-La-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/author-LWiJ3ebJ3gpU86_3bbLouw">Ái Tân Giác La Hoằng Lịch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Linh-Nh%E1%BA%A5t-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/H%E1%BA%A1ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-G49o-A5MVgGOIXtKtw0ByA">Hạng Vương miếu - 項王廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Linh-Nh%E1%BA%A5t-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-S7v5E_7ENdSDkZWf-yQ-nQ">Linh Nhất thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-K%E1%BB%B7/Hoan-nghinh-k%C3%ADnh-%C3%A1i-%C4%91%C3%ADch-Chu-t%E1%BB%95ng-l%C3%BD/poem-4qz3TFfE4PRVVGED9p3P1A">Hoan nghinh kính ái đích Chu tổng lý - 歡